{"tid":2110743,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"對啲剪片工或剪接工有興趣，有冇咩Course可以推介下？","createTime":"2020-07-16T06:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T13:02:49.000Z","uid":239684,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f8455ce2b6eaca711f01ab889b6bb79f1bb7b932","tid":2110743,"uid":239684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:19:41.000Z","msg":"有日突然有感，因為智能手機、平板，走出條街、公共車廂，大部份人都係拎住部手機睇野，而當中絕對睇片多過睇文字，突然有個想法：剪片可能喺未來(或者依都係)會係一個好common既技能，呀豬呀狗一個普通人都識up片上youtubezxab 於是喺黃金買左本Premiere Pro參考書喺屋企照住黎鋤，so for都做到一啲簡單野，upload到一啲叫做見得下人既野上youtube。<br />\n<br />\n隨住而黎就有啲想法，有興趣入啲media公司做想學下野，人工低啲都無妨，但發現好多公司都冇學徒呢啲post，於是有想進修的念頭，唔知有冇巴打會有啲partime diploma介紹下？<br />\n<br />\n(舊制中七畢業，會考有fullcert八科合格包括中英文)"},{"pid":"ffe84edb8de4d3806f014951afa8672cb9778947","tid":2110743,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"youtube 自學啦"},{"pid":"1bd706fb6cc5e6c949babf7b4b5fc8395c7c0593","tid":2110743,"uid":67346,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:21:32.000Z","msg":"人工低啲都無妨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n放心，呢行人工真係低到你唔信"},{"pid":"54bb9af81ae8a5613b9d96a2064d3fe9596a3f54","tid":2110743,"uid":239684,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1bd706fb6cc5e6c949babf7b4b5fc8395c7c0593","tid":2110743,"uid":67346,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:21:32.000Z","msg":"人工低啲都無妨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n放心，呢行人工真係低到你唔信"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:25:12.000Z","msg":"但起碼我覺得至少都係一門有少少專業技能既工作<br />\n唔似一啲文員仔咁，睇唔到自己價值喺邊"},{"pid":"c8d2b691e8b94a46bf215ab8b1ff1748fb7de2b9","tid":2110743,"uid"